QuestData.Title: Filling an Empty Throne
QuestData.Description:
Maw Walker.
In my long absence, you have done much to bring order and strength back to the necrolord covenant. In recognition, I invite you to witness a ceremony.
Return with me to my seat of power in Maldraxxus. It is time I rewarded one who was most loyal to our cause.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to the Seat of the Primus.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with the Primus at the Seat of the Primus.
